/wiki/Kiko_Rat\u00f3n: Francisco José González Expósito ( born 19 September 1976 ) , commonly known as Kiko Ratón , is a Spanish footballer who plays for CD Puerto Cruz as a striker . He amassed Segunda División totals of 166 matches and 27 goals over six seasons , representing in the competition Tenerife , Hércules and Girona .
/wiki/Orihuela_CF: Orihuela Club de Fútbol is a Spanish football team based in Orihuela , in the Valencian Community . Founded in 1993 it plays in Segunda División B - Group 3 , holding home games at Estadio Municipal Los Arcos , with a capacity of 7,000 seats .
/wiki/Girona_FC: Girona Futbol Club , S.A.D . is a professional football club based in Girona , Catalonia , Spain . Founded on 23 July 1930 , it plays in Segunda División . Girona holds its home matches at the 13,450-capacity Estadi Montilivi . The club also has youth and amateur women 's teams for competition .
/wiki/CF_Badalona: Club de Fútbol Badalona ( Catalan pronunciation : [ bəðəˈlonə ] ) is a Spanish football team based in Badalona , in the autonomous community of Catalonia . Founded in 1903 it plays in Segunda División B - Group 3 , temporarily holding home games at Estadi Municipal de Badalona , with a capacity of 4,170 seats .
/wiki/UDA_Gramenet: Unión Deportiva Atlético Gramenet Milán is a Spanish football team based in Santa Coloma de Gramenet , in the autonomous community of Catalonia . Founded in 1945 it currently plays in Segona Catalana - Group 4 , holding home games at Municipal de Sant Adrià in Sant Adrià de Besòs , with a capacity of 1,000 .
/wiki/Mat\u00edas_Alonso_Vallejo: Matías Damián Alonso Vallejo ( ; born 16 April 1985 ) is an Uruguayan footballer who plays for Club Atlético River Plate ( Montevideo ) as a forward .
/wiki/SD_Eivissa: Unión Deportiva Ibiza-Eivissa was a Spanish football team based in Ibiza Town , in the autonomous community of the Balearic Islands . Founded in 1995 , it last played in Regional de Ibiza , holding home matches at Estadi Can Misses , with a capacity of 10,000 seats .
/wiki/Joel_\u00c1lvarez: Joel Álvarez ( born March 2 , 1993 ) is a Spanish mixed martial artist who competes in the Lightweight division of the Ultimate Fighting Championship .
/wiki/CF_Gav\u00e0: Club de Futbol Gavà is a Spanish football team based in Gavà , in the autonomous community of Catalonia . Founded in 1922 it plays in Tercera División - Group 5 , holding home games at Estadi La Bòbila , with a capacity of 2,500 seats .
/wiki/CD_D\u00e9nia: Club Deportivo Dénia is a Spanish football team based in Dénia , in the autonomous community of Valencia . Founded in 1927 it plays in Divisiones Regionales de Fútbol in the Valencian Community , holding home games at Estadio Diego Mena Cuesta , with a capacity of 3.000 seats .
/wiki/\u00c1lvaro_del_Moral: Álvaro del Moral Galán ( born 9 May 1984 in Madrid ) is a Spanish footballer who plays for CD Buñol as a forward .
/wiki/Benidorm_CF: Benidorm Club de Fútbol was a Spanish football team based in Benidorm , in the autonomous community of Valencia . Founded in 1964 and dissolved in 2011 it held home matches at Estadio Municipal Guillermo Amor , which had a capacity of 6,000 .
